{"tid":2406461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽說PS5將在中國發售，日本玩家表示羨慕嫉妒恨！","createTime":"2021-02-13T08:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T02:47:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4f02d7bb7644174a29912b651b57a0f461068aad","tid":2406461,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"主要內容：<br />\n&quot;日本本土都缺貨，為什麼中國反而有貨？&quot;<br />\n&quot;比起日本更重視歐美中國市場，我覺得索尼已經不算是日企了！&quot;<br />\n「在增加銷售國家之前，至少應該先滿足日本國內的供應吧？」<br />\n「估計日本玩家今後要從中國郵購PS5了...」<br />\n「開什麼玩笑！日本國內都沒貨，還賣給中國...」<br />\n「希望別鎖區啊，否則估計又像Switch一樣不買國行反而跑來日本爆買日版...」<br />\n「別慌，聽說PS4中國特供版銷量慘淡，估計這次PS5也不會影響到日本國內」<br />\n「黃牛肯定又要大賺一筆了」"},{"pid":"57705f8a975c3c55561e73eae3f6eef7bb11f4b4","tid":2406461,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁玩？玩死海外市場！"},{"pid":"ad41caae6791f7b496241a7c8c3bbae2774e65e1","tid":2406461,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"日本PS5玩家也不少啊。為了搶購PS5，警察都出動了。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS5 日本繼續供不應求　秋葉原搶購亂象橫生一拍兩散<br />\n2021-01-30<br />\n自從去年 Sony 推出 PS5 以來，缺貨問題一直都存在，不只在香港，在「主場」日本亦一直供不應求。最近在秋葉原就有電器店開放現貨發售，但就引起搶購亂象。<br />\n<br />\n秋葉原的 Yodobashi 今日有現貨 PS5 發售，不過開售之後人潮就迫滿派籌的櫃檯，令派籌無法繼續進行，連櫃檯也有損毀，甚至需要出動警察維持秩序。結果 Yodobashi 決定取消今日的 PS5 現貨發售活動，需要再次考慮發售方式。有網民指在人群中有不少是中國人和專業炒家，抱怨他們令一般人無法購買。"},{"pid":"f304ff1911099cc0a9614c98637bdb9293c1b2ae","tid":2406461,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都是中國黃牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不是的，日本本國的黃牛也有很多。<br />\n之前囤積口罩的也大都是日本黃牛"},{"pid":"4e56b36028d343726512687126cef036f3001291","tid":2406461,"uid":127735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"中國出到PS6啦，點追<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dc79f4ed493e38e0fd4873d3544c88b0a79f84","tid":2406461,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"睇怕成年都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住兩年後出pro <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398f796ada1eb7b636c59b19712fb018892a44f9","tid":2406461,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾都搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a008364c01d670e82331c27c091b9fc6eb065df4","tid":2406461,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f7f506fb3b0200d5f1ee8927cb000db6eec39e","tid":2406461,"uid":6238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69dc79f4ed493e38e0fd4873d3544c88b0a79f84","tid":2406461,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"睇怕成年都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住兩年後出pro <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"加強版應該睇銷量 我覺得今年內都比較難用正價買到 舊<br />\n<br />\n機仲賣到唔會屎忽痕整部新機出黎 出部slim 就有機會 你<br />\n<br />\n見隔離switch 加強版咁耐都無聲氣就知"},{"pid":"fd921736b9d6b868c30f35d0c38026fa5db273ec","tid":2406461,"uid":115250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔係話有好多死貨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3279e76b5f19165b853a18f84dad0